=========================================================
Question 1 : Grade Evaluation
=========================================================

Write a Java program that accepts a student's grade
(A, B, C, or D) and displays the corresponding performance message.

Rules:
    A -> Excellent
    B -> Good
    C -> Average
    D -> Poor
    Any other value -> Invalid Grade

Task:
    1. Solve using Traditional Switch Statement.
    2. Refactor using Switch Expression.


