Question 2 : Day Finder
=========================================================

Write a Java program that accepts a day number (1-7)
and prints the corresponding day name.

Rules:
    1 -> Monday
    2 -> Tuesday
    3 -> Wednesday
    4 -> Thursday
    5 -> Friday
    6 -> Saturday
    7 -> Sunday
    Otherwise -> Invalid Day

Task:
    1. Solve using Traditional Switch Statement.
    2. Refactor using Switch Expression.


