Question 4 : Quarter Finder
=========================================================

Write a Java program that accepts a month number
(1 to 12) and determines in which quarter of the year
the month belongs.

Rules:
    Months 1,2,3    -> Q1
    Months 4,5,6    -> Q2
    Months 7,8,9    -> Q3
    Months 10,11,12 -> Q4

Any other value should display:
    Invalid Month

Task:
    1. Solve using Traditional Switch Statement.
    2. Refactor using Switch Expression.


