Question 5 : Traffic Signal Controller
=========================================================

Create an enum named TrafficSignal containing:

    RED
    YELLOW
    GREEN

Write a Java program that accepts a traffic signal
and displays the corresponding action.

Rules:
    RED    -> STOP
    YELLOW -> READY
    GREEN  -> GO

